T02TD1378E:264b-1: hri da ya badzra pa da n'a ma /
T02TD1378E:264b-3: snying po rdo rje'i tshig ces bya ba /
T02TD1378E:264b-4: lce rtse rkan sbyar rnal 'byor la ;
T02TD1378E:264b-5: / gcig tu brtson pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1378E:264b-6: dum bu ma yin dkyil 'khor gyi //
T02TD1378E:264b-7: rnam pa gang gis brtan g-yo khyab //
T02TD1378E:264b-8: gnas de gang gis bstan pa yi //
T02TD1378E:264b-9: dpal gyi bla ma de la 'dud //
T02TD1378E:264b-10: rdo rje'i nyi ma'ang gang sems ni //
T02TD1378E:264b-11: nor bu'i nang du son par blta //
T02TD1378E:264b-12: ye shes dkyil 'khor rnam pa yis //
T02TD1378E:264b-13: khams gsum po ni snang bar bya //
T02TD1378E:264b-14: phyag rgya gcig la mnyam sbyor dang //
T02TD1378E:264b-15: yang na phyag rgya bzhir sbyor ba //
T02TD1378E:264b-16: btsun mo'i grong du 'jug gyur kyang //
T02TD1378E:264b-17: sgyu ma'i sku ni rjes dran bya //
T02TD1378E:264b-18: snying po rdo rje'i tshig ri khrod zhabs kyis pandi ta nags kyi rin chen la gnang ba /
T02TD1378E:264b-19: de nyid dang lo chen bsod nams rgya mtsho'i sde'i 'gyur ro//
